// Dropdown
// Select dropdown with default value synchronization on mount and prop change.

useEffect syncs the internal selected value when the defaultValue prop changes.

FUNCTION handleChange(e)
  Updates internal selected state.
  Calls onChange with the newly selected option value.

---

FUNCTION Dropdown(props) -> ReactNode                                     EXPORT
  Renders a native select element with the provided options.
  Syncs to defaultValue via useEffect when the prop changes.
  Calls handleChange on selection.
